        <section eId="sec_12_223d">
          <num>12-223d</num>
          <heading>Assessments against one or more taxpayers in combined return</heading>
          <content>
            <p>Sec. 12-223d. Assessments against one or more taxpayers in combined return.In case a combined return is made as provided by section12-223a, the Commissioner of Revenue Services may assess the entire tax computed on the basis of such return against any one or more of the taxpayers covered by the return, in such proportions as he shall determine, but every such taxpayer shall be liable for the entire tax.
